column3: All I Know So Far: Setlist
column4:
Amazon release a live concert/documentary style film about P!nk, titled All I Know So Far, directed by Michael Gracey (The Greatest Showman).

The film will follow P!nk during her record-breaking 2019 Beautiful Trauma world tour, giving audiences a behind-the-scenes peek at her life on the road. The documentary delves into her attempts to balance being a Mum, a wife, a boss, and performer, featuring footage from P!nk’s 2018 Wembley performances which have never-before been released commercially.

In conjunction with the film release; P!nk will release the 16 track album ‘All I Know So Far’: Setlist will be released which will feature the brand new single, ‘All I Know So Far’, the AU Platinum ‘Cover Me In Sunshine’ as well as a variety of P!nk hits live

Twenty One Pilots have announced their new album, Scaled And Icy, which will be released via Fueled By Ramen!

The band has shared the forthcoming album’s first single, “Shy Away,” which is available on all streaming platforms and is accompanied by a Miles & AJ directed official music video.

Scaled And Icy is Twenty One Pilots’ first studio album in three years and follows their 2018 ARIA #1 debut LP, Trench.Standard Jewelcase Version

column3: Panasonic Lumix G100V Mirrorless Camera with 12-32mm Lens Kit + Tripod Grip
column4:
Overview

The primary focus of the G100 is to empower vloggers, influencers and social media natives to take their content to the next-level. It delivers high-resolution photos, razor-sharp 4K video and intelligent OZO Audio recording to equip content creators with the ability to tell their stories and engage with their audience.

Key Features

Compact. Lightweight. ConvenientWhether you’re filming a day in your life, or taking a quick selfie, the G100 is the perfect size to fit your lifestyle. A lightweight body and excellent ergonomics give you the confidence to shoot and film one-handed all day long. This camera kit includes a versatile 12-32mm f/3.5-5.6 ASPH. MEGA O.I.S. lens and Tripod Grip.

Detailed, High-Res Photos & Ultra-Sharp 4K VideoAt its heart, the G100 features a 20.3 megapixel MOS Image sensor that delivers vibrant, high- contrast photos and sharp, smooth 4K Video across a wide range of lighting conditions. The elimination of the low-pass filter helps to improve detail and sharpness to deliver flagship image quality.

Game Changing Audio RecordingThe OZO Audio recording built into the G100 is a revolutionary innovation for vloggers. The system developed by Nokia delivers rich, vibrant audio recording across a wide-range of shooting scenarios. Taking things, a step further, it has been combined with Panasonic’s Face and Eye Detect autofocus algorithms to intelligently optimise voice recording, even in noisy environments. Setting a new benchmark for built-in microphones, it eliminates the need for serious content creators to invest in a cumbersome external microphone.

Pixel Perfect Compositions & SelfiesThe free-angle LCD monitor is the ideal solution for vloggers. The articulating screen features a bright, 1840k dot high-resolution screen that is perfect for indoor and outdoor shooting. Eliminate the guess work when it comes to composition and focus in your vlogs or use the flip-out design to capture high and low angles with ease. For a more traditional shooting experience utilise the ultra-high resolution 3680k-dot electronic viewfinder.

Walk and Talk – Without the ShakeThe G100 Features a built-in gyro sensor that works in conjunction with your favourite O.I.S lenses to deliver sharper photos and smoother video. The all-new 5-Axis HYBRID I.S System* allows you to film on-the-go and take your friends, family and followers with you every step of the way.

Push Your Creative BoundariesThe dedicated S&Q Mode is your shortcut to capturing engaging Slow & Quick b-roll footage. The ability to slow down time with up to 4X 120fps Slow Motion or compress time with 8X Fast Motion Time-Lapse encourages you to see the world around you as a place with endless creative potential.The built-in V-Log L colour profile delivers professional level potential in post-production. V-Log L enables you to establish your own cinematic look by colour grading your footage without quality loss.

Immerse Your Audience on Your AdventureThe Video Selfie Mode makes it easy to tell your stories and share your experiences. It ensures both your face and the background remains in focus, eliminating distracting focus shifts and allowing you to concentrate on conveying your message to your viewers.

Convenient Content Creator FeaturesThe G100 features a range of innovative features that have been designed to help vloggers and modern creatives concentrate on doing what they love. The REC Frame Indicator makes forgetting to press the record a thing of the past, while the Frame Marker allows you to compose your shot in various aspect ratios to suit your preferred social platforms.

One-Button Sharing To Your SmartphoneSharing high quality footage with your audience is quicker and easier than ever before. Wi-Fi + Bluetooth connectivity and a dedicated smartphone button makes sending photos and video from the G100 to your smartphone a breeze. Automatic vertical video detection also eliminates the need to rotate footage you’ve specifically captured vertically, allowing you to use high quality clips for your Instagram and Facebook stories or TikToks immediately.

Get a Grip and Enhance Your Creative VersatilityLevel up your creative capabilities with the DMW-SHGR1 Grip. A popular accessory for vloggers everywhere, it combines an ergonomic grip with a mini tripod and remote recording functions to ensure you never miss a memorable moment. The use of a 3-way ball head makes the tripod function of the DMW-SHGR1 even more versatile. The grip offers confidence inspiring camera handling while the built-in tripod design is perfect for impromptu time lapses and long exposure shots. It’s the ultimate accessory to supercharge your b-roll footage and expand your creative output.

Automatically deep cleans carpets Dyson DLS™ technology inside the High Torque cleaner head monitors brush bar resistance 360 times a second, intelligently adapting power across different floor types automatically with no need to change cleaner heads5.

Hair screw tool – Picks up hair. Fast. With Dyson anti-tangle technology. Anti-tangle conical brush bar spirals hair off and into the bin to prevent wrapping of hair around the brush bar.

The right cleaning mode for the right task Three cleaning modes optimised for a variety of tasks. The right balance of power and run time, where you need it.

Advanced whole machine filtration The fully-sealed filtration system traps 99.99% of particles as small as 0.3 microns7.

‘Point and shoot’ hygienic bin emptying The ‘point and shoot’ mechanism hygienically ejects dust and debris into your bin, in one action –so there’s no need to touch the dirt.

Unique battery power management system Dyson’s power-optimising technology and battery-saving trigger help maximise run time, only using power when you need it.

Optional click-in battery pack Remove and replace at the press of a button for even longer cleans8.

Radial Cyclone™ technology 14 cyclones generate forces of 100,000g to fling dust into the bin without clogging the filter, so there’s no loss of suction.

Acoustically engineered Designed to absorb vibrations and dampen sound, to keep sound levels down.

Drop-in docking The Dyson V15™ vacuum drops into the wall-mounted dock, to charge it and tidily store tools. So it’s ready to grab and go.
